pageContext.claim: “It’s just nasty stuff. I never spoke to [Woodward]. Maybe I wasn’t given messages that he called.”
pageContext.analysis: The Washington Post released a recording and transcript of President Trump speaking to Bob Woodward about his book. During the call, he confirmed that Sen. Lindsey Graham (R-S.C.) mentioned an interview and Kellyanne Conway confirmed she tried to run the possibility through proper channels.
